ce suggest that they may be more prone to contradictions in the future.\n\n**Drill for Next Session:**\n\n**Exercise:** \"Verbal Transition Drill\"\n\n* Set a timer for 3 minutes.\n* Speak in a natural, conversational tone.\n* Introduce a new thought or idea every 10-15 seconds.\n* Practice pausing briefly before introducing each new idea.\n* Repeat the exercise 3-5 times, focusing on smooth verbal transitions.\n\nBy practicing this exercise, the candidate can develop the ability to communicate more confidently and smoothly, even in high-pressure situations.",
